menus.name: Potato Leek Soup

menus.name: Vegetable Soup

menus.name: Filet Mignon

menus.name: Ribeye Steak

menus.name: New York Strip
menus.description: Bold and robust, our New York Strip Steak boasts a firm texture and intense flavor, with a satisfyingly meaty bite.

menus.name: T-bone Steak

menus.name: Sirloin Steak

menus.name: Porterhouse Steak
menus.description: Our Porterhouse Steak is a carnivore's delight, featuring a generous portion of both tenderloin and strip steak, perfect for sharing or indulging.

menus.name: Prime Rib
menus.description: Juicy and succulent, our Prime Rib is slow-roasted to perfection, boasting rich flavor and melt-in-your-mouth tenderness.

menus.name: Skirt Steak
menus.description: Full of flavor and perfect for grilling, our Skirt Steak is known for its robust taste and juicy texture, making it a favorite among steak enthusiasts.

menus.name: Flat Iron Steak
menus.description: Tender and flavorful, our Flat Iron Steak is a versatile cut with rich marbling, offering a delicious beefy taste in every bite.

menus.name: Grilled Salmon

menus.name: Shrimp Scampi

menus.name: Lobster Tail

menus.name: Fish and Chips

menus.name: Crab Cakes

menus.name: Clam Linguine

menus.name: Seafood Paella

menus.name: Tuna Steak

menus.name: Scallop Risotto

menus.name: Bouillabaisse
